title: Does Pfizer ‘Page 132’ Warn Against Unprotected Sex After COVID-19 Vaccine?
subtitle: A "copypasta" meme stoked more fears about the COVID-19 vaccine on social media.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: Pfizer vaccine "page 132" warns not to have unprotected sex for 28 days after the second dose of the COVID-19 vaccine because "genetic manipulation" may cause birth defects.
